    'first-steps.text-3' => 'After you have installed the game, you will see the Metin2 symbol on your desktop. Additionally there will be an entry for Metin2 in the Windows start menu. Double click on the desktop symbol or choose an option from the start menu, to start the game. When necessary, Metin2 will update itself automatically to the newest version of the game, which may take several minutes.',
    'first-steps.text-4' => 'After the update you can fill in your account details and choose a game server. Subsequently you will have to choose from one of the three kingdoms and will then be able to create a character. Remember, that you can only use each character in the server in which you created it.',

    'tutorials.title' => 'Metin2 - Tutorials',
    'tutorials.text' => 'Welcome to the online MMORPG Metin2! After registering, you will learn more about the many kingdoms and possibilities of this online role-playing game. The detailed tutorial will explain how to find your way around the MMORPG and list the key combinations that will help you enjoy the fun and exciting gameplay.',
    'tutorials.create-character' => 'Create a character',
